{"id":396544,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/06/易寺礼：我目睹的清北招生怪相/","date":"2015-06-28T07:35:56Z","modified":"2015-09-13T12:44:34Z","title":"易寺礼：我目睹的清北招生怪相","content":"<div class=\"WB_text\"></div>\n<div class=\"WB_text\">来源：新浪微博</div>\n<div class=\"WB_text\"></div>\n<blockquote>\n<div class=\"WB_text\"><a class=\"W_fb S_txt1\" title=\"学术大观察\" href=\"http://www.weibo.com/u/5545466650?from=feed&amp;loc=nickname\" target=\"_blank\">@学术大观察</a>【我目睹的清北招生怪相】一年前我去招生，一个孩子分数很高，已经确定填报北大了，但是在专业上，妈妈认为女孩子读经管类容易就业，但是孩子想去读理科的专业。孩子说：“我要填北大物理”，妈妈说：“你要是敢填物理，我就不认你这个女儿”。一番僵持之下，当天没能填报志愿，回家之后…</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/0063idcujw1etjlhbxh7mj30hs8sju0x.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-396545\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2015/06/0063idcujw1etjlhbxh7mj30hs8sju0x.jpg\" alt=\"0063idcujw1etjlhbxh7mj30hs8sju0x\" width=\"440\" height=\"7834\" /></a></p>\n","author":1003,"categories":[18270,18269,9203,10466],"tags":[10755,9346,10227,23042,12529]}